{"tid":2448543,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"工聯會抗議確診者「社區游走」 美領館：假消息","createTime":"2021-03-16T03:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T05:44:03.000Z","uid":212249,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ca8354a8ea52f775d41109aaedee55b65b822cbc","tid":2448543,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T03:56:35.000Z","msg":"（獨媒報導）工聯會今早到美國駐港總領事館示威，連番諷美國應對疫情失敗、後知後感，促美國放下「高傲自尊心」，虛心學習良好的抗疫態度，又指相信如美國「唔知點樣做」，「我哋嘅祖國願意捨以援手。」美領館未有派員接信，工聯會將信件張貼在封鎖線外。<br />\n<br />\n他們稱領事館兩名確診的員工以外交豁免權為由，繼續在「社區游走」，表示強烈譴責。不過政府昨晚新聞公報已稱「美國駐香港總領事館一直全力配合政府上述各項防疫抗疫工作」，今早行政會議上，行政長官林鄭月娥亦稱兩人已經送院。領事館亦在社交媒體上斥人員未有配合防疫要求是「假消息。」"},{"pid":"8b52d8def7619f47173db46c3f6a8e08c9f4d659","tid":2448543,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T03:56:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1081445\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1081445&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=bf1e4d2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1081445&h=c88b24db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1081445</a>"},{"pid":"f74468d697ce288bbd7c45f60603cd108dd89f82","tid":2448543,"uid":2008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T03:59:47.000Z","msg":"搧動仇恨言論既假新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243d2a0088b5dc1a817b23ca4d39616444bc637c","tid":2448543,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T04:00:45.000Z","msg":"新田圍何偉俊😒😒😒"},{"pid":"9adc685dd45a896025ea5e851bc7b9ea8dfc2183","tid":2448543,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T04:35:42.000Z","msg":"忠誠既癈柴唔好碌出嚟做on9嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ffd0fc7c6f63b5b422c423defdcc9acc0c92dc","tid":2448543,"uid":75256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202